targets.query: SELECT last("uptime") FROM "system" WHERE  "host" =~ /^$host$/
SELECT last("n_cpus") FROM "system" WHERE  "host" =~ /^$host$/
SELECT last("available_percent") FROM "mem" WHERE  "host" =~ /^$host$/
SELECT last("free") AS "value" FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/

SELECT  non_negative_derivative(mean("bytes_recv"), 1s) *8 AS "Bytes recv", non_negative_derivative(mean("bytes_sent"), 1s) *8 AS "Bytes sent" FROM "net" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "interface" =~ /^$interface$/ AND "interface" != 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), interface

SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(packets_recv),1s) AS "in_pps", non_negative_derivative(mean(packets_sent),1s) AS "out_pps" FROM "net" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "interface" =~ /^$interface$/ AND "interface" != 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), interface
SELECT mean(*) FROM "netstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean(bytes_recv) AS "Bytes recv", mean(bytes_sent) AS "Bytes send" FROM "net" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "interface" =~ /^$interface$/ AND "interface" != 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), interface
SELECT last(/.*_cpu_usage/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean(/.*_cpu_usage/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "testcase" =~ /^$testcase$/ AND "PT_project" =~ /^$pt_project$/ AND "testsuite" =~ /^$testsuite$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean(/.*_cpu_usage/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "testcase" =~ /^$testcase$/ AND "PT_project" =~ /^$pt_project$/ AND "testsuite" =~ /^$testsuite$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(/.*_memory_rss$/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean(/.*_memory_rss$/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "testcase" =~ /^$testcase$/ AND "PT_project" =~ /^$pt_project$/ AND "testrun" =~ /^$testrun$/ AND "testsuite" =~ /^$testsuite$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(/.*_num_threads/) FROM "mpx_procstat" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(/^.*usage.*$/) FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(*) FROM "mem" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(total) AS "Total swap" FROM "swap" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last(used) AS "Used swap" FROM "swap" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(read_bytes),1s) as "read" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sda|sdb$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(write_bytes),1s) as "write" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sdb|sda$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT last("iops_in_progress") AS "iops in progress"  FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" = 'sda' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT last("iops_in_progress") AS "iops in progress"  FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" = 'sdb' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(read_time),1s) as "read_time" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /(v|s)d(a|b|c|d)$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(write_time),1s) as "write_time" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /(v|s)d(a|b|c|d)$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(io_time),1s) as "io_time" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /(v|s)d(a|b|c|d)$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT last("total") AS "total", last("used") AS "used", last("free") AS "free" FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY path,  time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(reads),1s) as "sda_read" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sda/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(writes),1s) as "sda_write" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sda/  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(reads),1s) as "sdb_read" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sdb/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean(writes),1s) as "sdb_write" FROM "diskio" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "name" =~ /sdb/  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT last("await") FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "device" = 'sda' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("await") FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "device" = 'sdb' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("pct_util") FROM "disk" WHERE "device" = 'sda' AND "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("pct_util") FROM "disk" WHERE "device" = 'sdb' AND "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
